rent education fund allocation please see your hr manager for the appropriate form when can i use them each year stap funds are made available on september 1st and will run out on august 31 each september the university replenishes your stap funds unused stap funds do not carry over to the following fiscal year so you should be sure to use them during the current academic year if you are registering for a fall course prior to sept 1st we will accept your registration request to use stap funds for the upcoming year your stap request will be held and then submitted to the stap office after september 1 how can i use them during the registration process you can apply your stap funds in the tuition assistance section on our website you ll be asked to provide the 8 digit university id number found on your photo employee id card if you are using stap funds for the first time continuing studies will need to verify your employment before accessing your stap funds if your account has not been enabled your balance will show as zero and prompt you to pay with a credit card if this happens please email our office continuingstudies stanford edu so that we can set up your stap funds in our system how to check your balance please be sure to verify your stap eligibility and that you have sufficient stap funds before enrolling in a course to check eligibility and your stap balance online go to http axess stanford edu and login with your sunet id click on the stars tab and then my stap balance what can stap funds pay for courses you can use your stap funds toward continuing studies course tuition registration fee and any applicable course fees textbooks in many cases you can purchase textbooks required for continuing studies courses and get reimbursed through your stap funds for further details please consult with the person in your department who handles reimbursements need more information many helpful answers to your questions about stap can be found by visiting stanford's stap page on the human resources website found at this link http hreap stanford edu stap html please note that your registration in continuing studies courses will not be final until we receive confirmation from human resources of your stap eligibility and balance 2012 stanford university all rights reserved home site map university policies mla program instructor login help
